# Success a string

Strings can also increment like numbers

<pre class="ruby">str = 'a'
str.succ! # => 'b'
'xxy'.succ # => "xxz"
</pre>

#### Also UTF-8 based string can be also incremented

<pre class="ruby">'хорошо'.succ # => "хорошп"
</pre>
